title: Tom Hanks Warns of Dental Ad Using A.I. Version of Him
description: Mr. Hanks and the CBS anchor Gayle King both said their likenesses were used in unauthorized advertisements, as worries have grown over the unregulated use of artificial intelligence.

title: Microsoft C.E.O. Testifies That Google’s Power in Search Is Ubiquitous
description: Satya Nadella, the chief executive of Microsoft, is the government’s biggest-name witness in its landmark antitrust case against Google.

title: Who’s Rooting Hardest for a Sam Bankman-Fried Conviction? The Crypto Industry.
description: Crypto insiders, who have been trying to distance themselves from the FTX founder, are united in their zeal to see Mr. Bankman-Fried held to account.

title: Crypto Goes on Trial, as Sam Bankman-Fried Faces His Reckoning
description: The FTX founder’s uphill court battle starts Tuesday, after he has come to symbolize everything that went wrong with the cryptocurrency industry.

title: How a Pricing Change Led to a Revolt by Unity’s Video Game Developers
description: In an industry where customers are slow to trust and quick to criticize, a new fee from Unity infuriated studios that use its platform.
